ec2 machine and enable ssh. https, http, port 8501

AWS+GCP+AI ATS SYSTEM

PART-1 AWS EC2 UBUNTU INSTANCE
LAUNCH A NEW EC2 INSTANCE
UBUNTU SERVER 20.04 LTS
ALLOWING ESSENTIAL PORT ie-8501

PART2 APPLICATION INSTALLATION
step-1 update & install python 3.7+ and pip
       sudo apt update && sudo apt install python3 python3-pip python3-venv -y
step-2 install git 
sudo apt install git -y
step-3 install Poppler (for pdf to image)
install Poppler
step-4 
sudo apt install poppler-utils -y

PART-3 SET UP THE ATS APPLICATION
step-1 - git clone https://
ls
step-2 cd application-tracking-system
step-3 set up a virtual environment
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
step-4 install project dependencies
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install google-generativeai

PART-4 AI Gemini setup 
get Gemini API key from Google cloud platform (GCP)
go to google cloud console & create project asearch gemini apiaclick on gemini api ----> manage ---->Generative Language API ->credentials->create credentials->get api

PART-5
Connect AWS ATS application with GCP Gemini AI
1. add the API Keyto Streamlit Secret
mkdir -p .streamlit
vi .streamlit/secret.toml

GOOGLE_API_KEY = "your api key"
2. Run the Streamlit app
streamlit run app.py --server.port 8501 --server.enableCORS false


